_sText:
in English:
de_saunatupa is a one bombsite map that is partially based on a popular map layout "rantasauna". Most of these maps in CS:S had many problems and missing details, such as lighting. So I wanted to make my version out of the layout. I made this map completely from a new file and built it from my memory, while making some additions and differences. The map has 14 playerstarts per team, cubemaps(reflections), soundscapes and a 3D skybox.

in Finnish:
de_saunatupa on perus saunamappi, joka perustuu osittain suositun rantasauna mapin pohjaan. Näitä mappeja on kuitenkin CS Sourcessa monta erilaista, eikä yhtä kunnollista porttia alkuperäisesta CS 1.6 mapista, joten tein mapin osittain muistista ja omilla ideoilla.
